0.Instruction: Sit at a table with a pink and a yellow post-its in front of you.

1.Instruction: Rest your right hand on the table.

2.Instruction: With your left hand, place the pink post-it at the edge of the table away from you.

3.Instruction: With your left hand, place the yellow post-it at the edge of the table right in front of you.

4.Instruction: Position your right hand on the yellow post-it.

5.Instruction: Reach forward with your right hand to touch the pink post-it by extending your elbow. Use your left hand to assist in moving right hand if needed.

6.Instruction: Return your hand again to the yellow post-it.

7.Instruction: Reach forward with your right hand to touch the pink post-it by extending your elbow. Use your left hand to assist in moving right hand if needed.

8.Instruction: Return your hand again to the yellow post-it.

9.Instruction: Rest your hand on the table.
